OL,3,CDaughter jailed for stealing over
OL,4,C#250,000 from mother with dementia
OL,6,FA daughter who defrauded her
OL,7,Fvulnerable mother out of more than
OL,8,F#250,000 has been sentenced to two
OL,9,Fyears in prison by Guernsey's Royal
OL,10,FCourt.
OL,12,FChristine Peet, 65, had been appointed
OL,13,Fas her mother's guardian after she was
OL,14,Fdiagnosed with dementia in September
OL,15,F2020 and was therefore responsible for
OL,16,Fmanaging her financial affairs.
OL,18,FHer mother's house was sold when she
OL,19,Fwas no longer able to care for herself.
