OL,3,CDaughter jailed for stealing over
OL,4,C#250,000 from mother with dementia
OL,6,FIn October 2021, Peet transferred
OL,7,F#250,000 to herself and went on to use
OL,8,Fthe funds over the next two years for
OL,9,Fher own and others' gain.
OL,11,FPeet's criminal behaviour only came to
OL,12,Flight when she made an application for
OL,13,Fsupport from the States of Guernsey to
OL,14,Fpay for her mother's ongoing nursing
OL,15,Ffees when the money had run out.
